flowchart TD
  A[User opens Transition Portal] --> B[Authenticate and load role]
  B --> C{Persona}
  C -->|Staff| D[View property details and own training]
  C -->|Owner| E[View property details and all staff training]
  C -->|CMC| F[View assigned properties and first-call queue]
  C -->|Admin| G[Assign/reassign property to CMC]
  D --> H[Request follow-up call]
  E --> H
  F --> I[Schedule mandatory first call]
  G --> J[Active CMC assignment updated]
  J --> K[Future scheduled calls transferred or recreated]
  H --> L[Find CMC free slots via Outlook]
  I --> L
  L --> M[User selects slot]
  M --> N[Create Zoom meeting]
  N --> O[Create Outlook calendar event]
  O --> P[Persist call record]
  P --> Q[Queue confirmation and reminders]
  Q --> R[Notification sent by email/SMS]
  R --> S[Call completed or rescheduled]
  S --> T[Transition status updated]
